=== Overview

This group is provided to add vndk support in AndroidBoard.mk

==== Options

--- true
use this option to enable VNDK with the flag "BOARD_VNDK_VERSION".

--- false
use this option to be compatible with full treble, create vndk and vndk-sp folder.

--- none
use this option to do nothing.

--- default
when not explicitly selected in mixin spec file, the default option will be used same as none.
